    "title": "清風明月",
    "enTitle": "A Clear and Beautiful Night",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "シンボリルドルフとお出かけをし、\r\n少し遅くなった帰り道にて――",
            "enText": "The day is growing late as Symboli<n>Rudolf and I\nhead back after our day<n>out.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 3996872218033827417
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -3553952558420145727
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2339138954237231646,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "トレーナー君。\r\n帰る前に寄りたい所があるのだが……。",
            "enText": "If you wouldn't mind, there's somewhere<n>I would\nlike to drop by before we return<n>to the academy.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 62,
            "voiceIdx": 55,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": -1889122586916980110
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": -8117550344881548144
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6084716497726407501,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "よければ、一緒に来てもらえないだろうか。",
            "enText": "Would you be willing to accompany me?",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いいけど、どこにいくんだ？",
                    "enText": "Sure, where are we going?",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "いいけど、どこにいくの？",
                    "enText": "Sure, where are we going?",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -5116410584293705408
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 17,
                    "pathId": -2802807724365846488
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3921397658120558961,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "いやなに。今日は、\r\n三日月が綺麗に見えそうなのでな――",
            "enText": "The moon is supposed to be a perfect<n>crescent\ntonight, and I hear that the sky<n>will be clear...",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": 2822390329306391808
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 49,
                    "pathId": -2924806172279031853
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1962226560051230690,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "シンボリルドルフに連れられて\r\nやってきたのは、高台にある神社だった。",
            "enText": "Symboli Rudolf leads me to a shrine<n>located on a\nsmall hill.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": 6152593577735032863
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 2114141968328263444
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3111686398562847479,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "ここは遮蔽物や明かりも少なくてね、\r\n月がとても綺麗に見えるんだ。",
            "enText": "There aren't any buildings or bright<n>lights around\nhere. We should have a<n>perfect view.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "voiceIdx": 59,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 5552425488843855726
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": -2830791551607003313
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": -9174021942102502648
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3103968863834755112,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "見上げると確かに、\r\n綺麗な三日月が夜空に煌々と浮かんでいた。",
            "enText": "Perfect is right. A beautiful crescent<n>moon shines\nbrightly in the sky above us.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": -3472392153075422926
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": 162654730093223063
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": -453586835430654908
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5950944197474973457,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "……これは、あまり\r\n話に出したことはないのだが。",
            "enText": "I rarely speak about this, but...",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "pathId": 7796051391746548569,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "幼い頃の私は、この髪の色形にちなんで、\r\n『ルナ』と呼ばれていたことがあるんだ。",
            "enText": "When I was young, I was often called<n>Luna, on\naccount of the white streak in<n>my hair.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "pathId": -2559528477731362219,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "……意外な響きか？\r\nまぁ、幼名みたいなものだよ。",
            "enText": "You could hardly imagine it now, could<n>you? But\nit suited me then.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": 7967912417108721966
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -3013654162366158008
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1259878277058763131,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "当時の私はその名で呼ばれるのが好きでね……\r\n由来を聞いてからは、月を見る度、喜んだよ。",
            "enText": "I always loved the sound of it, and once<n>I learned\nwhere it came from, I smiled<n>every time I caught\nsight of the moon.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -2972196360684313427
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": -7553422820139193595
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8815921220772191942,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "だが――",
            "enText": "...But that's in the past now.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 47,
            "voiceIdx": 79,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": 2103276961726114863
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": -1558126377788566432
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3156678411160916842,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "私が帝道を往く決意をしてからは、\r\nその名で呼ばれることは、無くなった。",
            "enText": "I left that name behind when I resolved<n>to walk\nthe path of the Emperor.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 3164342227974497346
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": 3325432623322120696
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2391026537423651849,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "……別に、それを寂しく\r\n思っているわけではないよ。",
            "enText": "That isn't to say I mourn its loss, you<n>understand.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "voiceIdx": 50,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -3529280316782387092
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 19,
                    "pathId": -4665702006919781093
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5809753934317291087,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "ただ、どういう訳か――\r\n君には、話しておきたくなったんだ。",
            "enText": "I can't explain why, but... I simply felt<n>that you\nought to know.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "voiceIdx": 35,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "教えてもらえて嬉しい",
                    "enText": "I'm glad you told me.",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "可愛い名前だ",
                    "enText": "It's a pretty name.",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "可愛い名前だね",
                    "enText": "It's a pretty name.",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "これから先も、ずっと覚えておく",
                    "enText": "I won't forget it.",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": -6136702856704566133
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 4251581238607144617
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8809897490902056132,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "ただ、どういう訳か――\r\n君には、話しておきたくなったんだ。",
            "enText": "I can't explain why, but... I simply felt<n>that you\nought to know.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "voiceIdx": 35,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "教えてもらえて嬉しい",
                    "enText": "I'm glad you told me.",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "可愛い名前だ",
                    "enText": "It's a pretty name.",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "可愛い名前だね",
                    "enText": "It's a pretty name.",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "これから先も、ずっと覚えておく",
                    "enText": "I won't forget it.",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": -3249407203917112106
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -8230973749291940457
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9136749532520015942,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "私も、君に聞いてもらえて嬉しいよ。",
            "enText": "I'm glad that you were so willing to<n>listen.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": 5518524193790466814
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": 1202105465223852447
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8689778038237716706,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "――ああ。\r\nなんだろうな。",
            "enText": "I feel... How should I put it?",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 54,
            "voiceIdx": 59,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": -7160756362395895781
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 12,
                    "pathId": 8849671288629803634
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7213286560916010703,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "どこか胸がすくような――\r\nこの夜空のような、清々しい心持ちだ。",
            "enText": "It's as if a burden has been lifted from<n>my\nshoulders. My heart feels as clear as<n>the night air.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -8891321052887362268
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 28,
                    "pathId": 2481497080255155287
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4272212979168934027,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "……帰ろう。トレーナー君。",
            "enText": "...We ought to head back.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 53,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": 553402007711530772
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 12,
                    "pathId": -1358674634940775881
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -301852054964334547,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "明日からも……隣を頼む。",
            "enText": "I'm counting on you, Trainer. Tomorrow<n>and\nbeyond...",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 52,
            "voiceIdx": 39,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": 3848234695816754288
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": -8579515978221169961
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9134708229306147173,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女の話してくれた思い出も一緒に抱えて、\r\n明日からも隣にいようと心に誓った。",
            "enText": "With the memory she shared still fresh in<n>my\nmind, I quietly swear to stay by<n>Symboli Rudolf's\nside.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 70,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 2244407125199742098
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 6967685076860628875
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1287663197586701908,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "ふっ。可愛いからって、\r\n人前では呼んでくれるなよ。",
            "enText": "Hah. Be that as it may, call me that in<n>public and\nyou'll sound like a lunatic.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": 2033894921959323892
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -452484410752590136
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8216693520657772691,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "…………む？",
            "enText": "...Oh!",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 48,
            "voiceIdx": 26,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": -321673485159588484
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": -1722558140387818028
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 22,
                    "pathId": -8365313885446151187
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5533135841289870714,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "人前では、呼んで――\r\nふふっ、なるほどな。",
            "enText": "Call me Luna, and you'll sound like...<n>Pffft. That's\nrather good.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 59,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "どうした？",
                    "enText": "What is it?",
                    "nextBlock": 26
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "どうしたの？",
                    "enText": "What is it?",
                    "nextBlock": 26
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -2266629772116675010
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": 6653619880617102121
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": -2822301488407892238
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8329717230527201951,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "ルナと、呼んでくれルナ……。",
            "enText": "Luna... Lunatic...",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 54,
            "voiceIdx": 34,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": 4703057091397124795
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 27,
                    "pathId": 4034996977347435500
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6586400755353650096,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "くふっ、これはいいぞ。\r\n君にしか、通じないという意味でもね。",
            "enText": "That's some quality wordplay. Perfect for<n>an\ninside joke between comrades.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -6768691483208082621
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 49,
                    "pathId": -6978642313147401644
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5543129013062211330,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ツボに入って笑いを我慢する彼女と共に、\r\n月明かりの下、学園まで帰った。",
            "enText": "We walk back to the academy under the<n>\nmoonlight, with Symboli Rudolf stifling<n>giggles all\nthe while.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -8138005798803695341
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -2908221564112379112
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 623757659802181436,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "…………安心したよ。",
            "enText": "That... means a lot to me.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 4738401669983098741
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 25,
                    "pathId": -1412069507436354110
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4660102726539613094,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "いつか私が、この道の果てに辿り着き、\r\n理想を体現した後も――",
            "enText": "It's reassuring to think that, even after I<n>have\nwalked my path to its end and<n>made my dreams a\nreality...",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 3090270751091505614
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": 2271588270964626044
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5038339291182508879,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "君が、そこに到るまでの私を、\r\n覚えていてくれている。",
            "enText": "You will still remember who I used to be.",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 62,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
